'''Statiu''' a [[Skolpcha|skolpcha]] we riprizent wan or muo smadi ar animal (ingkluudn abschrak kansep aligarikali riprizent az piipl ar animal), naamali ful-lent, az opuoz tu a [[Bos (skolpcha)|bos]], ah akliis nier tu laif-saiz, ar laaja.<ref>Merriam Webster's Dictionary difain statiu az: "wah chrii-dimenshanal riprizentieshan yuujali a smadi, animal, ar mitikal biin we eh-projuus bai skolpcharin, maglin, ar kyaasin" [http://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/statue]</ref>  Sumaal statiu, yuujali likl anof fi kiah pikop, kaal a '''statyuet''' ar figariin.

Di definishan a statiu no aalwiez klier-kot; [[Ikueschrian skolpcha|ikueschrian statiu]] a smadi a-raid aas, soertnli ingkluud, ah ina nof kies, laka [[Madana ah Pitni|Madana ah Pitni]] ar [[Pieta|Pieta]], skolpcha a tuu smadi wi kount azwel.

Statiu eh-projuus ina nof kolcha frah [[Bifuo-Ischri|bifuo-ischri]] tu di prezant; di uolis nuo statiu diet tu bout 30,000 ier ago. Di wol taalis statiu, [[Spring Templ Buda|Spring Templ Buda]], a 420 fut (128 m), ah ilokiet ina Lushan Kounti, Henan, Chaina.

